byline.original: By JUSTIN SABLICH and JASON SABLICH

abstract: We are teaming with FantasyPros.com to analyze the toughest fantasy matchups for Week 7. Vote on who you think is the right pick.

lead_paragraph: Jason and Justin Sablich are here to help you with your fantasy football team. The Sablich brothers will provide fantasy football advice throughout the season on this blog and on Twitter (@5thDownFantasy).
